high_descs: Turn right and go to the stove.
Pick up the pot from the front of the stove.
Turn left and take the pot past the sink.
Set the pot down on the left side of the sink.
Put the apple in the pot on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Get the pot and put the apple inside of it next to the sink.

high_descs: Move forward then turn to your right head to the stove
Pick up the pot on the stove
Turn to your left and move forward then face on the counter beside the microwave
Put the pot on the counter beside the microwave
Pick up the apple in the sink
Put the apple inside the pot
anns.task_desc: Put the apple in the pot

high_descs: Walk to the right side of the stove on your right.
Pick up the pot on the front burner of the stove.
Cross the room and stand to the left of the sink facing the counter.
Place the pot on the counter next to the microwave.
Pick up the apple on the far left of side of the sink.
Place the apple inside the pot that is next the the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Take an apple in a pot next to the microwave.
